{"tid":1306645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再推（希望原作者睇到）】＜金鐘宣言 / The Admiralty Declaration＞終極ver.","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:19:30.000Z","uid":121855,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e31db5cc6835573277e8c3c7c59ed7a62e69c209","tid":1306645,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"我見既然仲未煲得起 應該趕得切掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到目前為止流傳既版本既英文好多錯漏 如果要落歷史唔能夠直出 所以我執左呢個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於中文我就冇乜改動 留返比原作者自己做最後決定 但係我唔知係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n--------<br />\n<strong>＜金鐘宣言 / The Admiralty Declaration＞</strong><br />\n<ins>香港人民爭取其應有之普世價值及社會制度之公開宣言</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 對於過去數日，以至近數年之港人抗爭運動，皆為香港人為爭取自己應有的權利，所作出之公民抗命活動，所有熱愛香港的人民將一直支持此等抗爭直到永遠。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Regarding to the recent series of protests and civil disobedience acts, we the people who love Hong Kong shall continue to fight for our rights until the end of time.</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 謹代表香港人民宣誓，香港人民將永遠以追求本來應有之普世價值及社會制度為己任。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">On behalf of all HongKongers, we shall never cease pursuing the universal values and social system that we once already had, and, that we suppose to have.</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 對於行政，立法，司法機關等腐敗，香港人民已無法容忍，若不立即進行改革，人民必將舉起手中的武器及盾牌，推翻暴政，推翻議會。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We no longer stand the injustice of our government. We shall raise our arms to overthrow the puppet-like Legislative Council if the government is not putting her face on it.</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 沒有民主選舉是一切問題之根源，必須馬上修改立法會議席及行政長官產生辦法，若非落實全民普選，誓不罷休。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The lacking in referendum is in fact the root of all current evils. Until a universal suffrage of the Chief Executive, with a fair election system of the LegCo members is to happen, we shall never stand down.</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 各大政府組織內部腐敗不堪，要求相關領導人士立即道歉，下台。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Principal officials related shall demonstrate the accountability, by disbanding the governance team and stepping down with sincere apologies.</span><br />\n<br />\n6. 要求政府立即釋放相關被捕示威者及政治犯，還他們一個清白。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The government must relinquish all charges against arrested protestors, as well to stop creating a &ldquo;White Terror&rdquo; atmosphere by exercising a mass political score-settling.</span><br />\n<br />\n7. 政府必須承諾追究警隊以不當武力鎮壓示威者，警隊必須向全港市民致歉。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The government must promise to conduct a full and fair investigation on police brutality. The Police Force must immediately admit its liability for the inappropriate conducts.</span><br />\n<br />\n8. 於立法會提出議案，必須將近年運動定性為公民抗命民主運動，而非暴動。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Concerning on recent protests, the term &ldquo;riot&rdquo; shall be retracted to democratic movements, or disturbance at the most.</span><br />\n<br />\n9. 無限感激所有為香港未來付出鮮血和生命的人民英雄。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">On behalf of all HongKongers, we wish to express our sincere gratitude to all of those who have paid their effort, blood, or even life for Hong Kong&rsquo;s future.</span><br />\n<br />\n10. 毋忘香港血色六月。要求立法將6月9日定為香港法定紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall never forget June of 2019. This bloody yet beautiful month shall go down in the history of Hong Kong, with 9th of June becoming an official memorial day.</span>"},{"pid":"2de895f145b610b482a1b3156cdd1c5b110deb65","tid":1306645,"uid":16713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0da543ee60e1b4f90c3da3f1905f308045ef62a","tid":1306645,"uid":121855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"限定自推一次咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37c3241f6f7a8754b4da74f5582f5f440c9e842","tid":1306645,"uid":41908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit